
 <div class="stx">
  <p>经过几个月的规划和辛苦的工资，组建小组的成员很高兴的在这里宣布Plone基金（Plone
  Foundation）的成立.</p>

  <p>这个基金，将在多方面使得我们的社区受益:</p>

  <ul>
   <li>Plone的市场化和宣传、传播<br />
   Marketing and evangelization of Plone</li>

   <li>开发支持<br />
   Development support</li>

   <li>法律支持<br />
   Legal support</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Plone基金模仿开源世界的一些成功案例建立，如Apache 软件基金（Apache Software
  Foundation）. 她将拥有Plone的版权和商标，她的任务是：<b>保护和提升Plone。</b><br />
  The Plone Foundation is modeled after similar successful
  ventures in the Open Source world, such as the Apache Software
  Foundation. It will own the copyrights and trademarks for
  Plone, and its mission is to <b>Protect and Promote
  Plone</b>.</p>

  <p>
  Plone团队很高兴的看到这个组织的建立，我们建议你查看基金的更多信息：如果你是一个Plone的用户或者开发人员，Plone基金将如何帮助你，以及你如何去支持这个基金。<br />

  The Plone Team is delighted to see this organization being
  established, and we encourage you to find out more about the
  Foundation, and how it will help you as a Plone
  user/developer, and how you can support the Foundation.</p>

  <p><b>附加的新闻</b>: Plone基金很高兴的宣布我们的初始合作伙伴, <span class="link-external"><a href="http://www.ca.com">CA公司（Computer
  Associates）</a></span>.</p>

  <p>更多的信息:</p>

  <ul>
   <li>访问 <a href="http://plone.org/foundation">Plone基金网站</a>.</li>

   <li>阅读<a href="http://plone.org/foundation/about/pr/formation">Plone基金成立新闻稿</a>.</li>
  </ul>新闻出处：<a href="http://plone.org/foundation/announcement">Plone.org</a>
 </div>
